reviewText: this was so so stupid omg why did they even make this the Japanese are really out there. def the worst out of all 4 of the dvds

I saw this quite a long time ago and loved it! A great way to close the doors on a great series.

STORY: A tranny doctor named Peter is one of the craziest and most dangerous persons in Japan. He goes around killing people, cutting them up and feeding them to other people. The rest... you don't wanna know.

THOUGHTS: A great film. Filled with comedy and gore! Just how like it!

So buy this!
